{"type":"message","id":"28acec4a","parentId":"fb2d50a7","timestamp":"2026-03-23T06:07:27.901Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:body-repair-2026 人体修复能力思考推送] 思考人类如何进化身体的修复能力。比如牙齿再生、器官自愈、细胞修复等前沿研究方向。每次分享一个有趣的角度或发现。发送到微信：510723047\nCurrent time: Monday, March 23rd, 2026 — 14:07 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-23 06:07 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774246047894}}
